Name: rer.portlet.er_navigation
Version: 1.0.7
Summary: A custom navigation portlet for ER portal
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/
Author: RedTurtle Technology
Author-email: sviluppoplone@redturtle.net
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        A custom navigation portlet that:
        
        * add a customizable CSS class
        * set default toplevel to 0
        * the title will not appear if not set
        * title's link is the root set in the portlet
        
        Credits
        =======
        
        Developed with the support of `Regione Emilia Romagna`__; Regione Emilia Romagna supports the `PloneGov initiative`__.
        
        __ http://www.regione.emilia-romagna.it/
        __ http://www.plonegov.it/
        
